ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地wfc"},{"pid":"1470a058392cbb4de007ed3634680eefa553832a","tid":1552431,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0495fa5999a0106821ac1e13f8b9c52d3b56abab","tid":1552431,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:12:50.000Z","msg":"到今日仲話玩火會失民意果啲真係岸撚鳩<br />\n香港 玩左成個月 玩到慣哂 民意有變過？<br />\n國際 人地對示威既認知就係玩火搶野無差別攻擊<br />\n我地岩岩先到玩火 人地覺得好平常同示威終於升級<br />\n再講我地玩火從來都無攞黎攻擊人 只係路障<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意分化撚收皮啦你地</span></span>"},{"pid":"48f07e4538c71940a10b5682160713042345c3b2","tid":1552431,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b739d6ac8297d514a278c703db08035be1b81f","tid":1552431,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ecd8b01863c02432b40aaf029c04b14e22a941","tid":1552431,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"經過831真係大部分人都歸邊 <br />\n不過文宣最近真係少"},{"pid":"d5799f7b523bb189a98b2e1e1586546126379bdd","tid":1552431,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2feae439f0c23782357c41cb5689b68b11854185","tid":1552431,"uid":175731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"講真，搞地鐵關佢地撚事，唔好搞到人地地方領事館咪得"},{"pid":"5739bebc36dfdeac939a607416c4ed1617e7534b","tid":1552431,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab7a5ad0248a7183882ceb6064e681e88d5f6955